---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="AI Engineering" description="Study notes on RAG, loop engineering, and enterprise AI implementation.">
  <section class="hero">
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">AI Engineering</p>
      <h1>Notes on building useful AI systems.</h1>
      <p>
        This section is for AI engineering notes that are not mainly about coding-agent productivity. The focus is
        how organizations and products can use AI systems better.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="meta-box">
      <strong>Planned topics</strong>
      <span>RAG, loop engineering, evaluation, reliability, and human-in-the-loop workflows.</span>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="grid">
      <article class="card">
        <div class="badge-row">
          <span class="badge blue">Planned</span>
        </div>
        <h2>RAG</h2>
        <p>Learning notes on retrieval, indexing, chunking, reranking, citation, freshness, and knowledge maintenance.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="card">
        <div class="badge-row">
          <span class="badge blue">Planned</span>
        </div>
        <h2>Loop Engineering</h2>
        <p>Notes on feedback loops, evaluation loops, self-improving systems, and workflow-level AI reliability.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
